browser_narrative.complexity_income: Egypt is as complex as expected for its income level.
browser_narrative.eci_rank_change: Egypt's economy has become less complex, worsening 3 positions in the ECI ranking.
browser_narrative.complexity_driver: Egypt's worsening complexity has occurred in spite of the increasing diversification of its exports, as the country has diversified into lower complexity products.
browser_narrative.growth_projection: Egypt is projected to grow moderately. 4.0% annually, ranking in the top quartile of countries globally.
browser_narrative.opportunities: Egypt is positioned to take advantage of many opportunities to diversify its production using its existing knowhow.
